data.description: Welcome to 3284 Mira Monte Dr., San Bernardino, CA. This exceptional 3 bedroom, 2.5-bath home, spanning an impressive 1,932 sq. ft., graces a sprawling lot of 16,068 sq. ft., offering an abundance of space and possibilities. Your arrival is welcomed by a two-car attached garage, seamlessly blending convenience with style. The main level offers a formal living room adorned with a charming fireplace, setting the stage for cozy gatherings. The adjacent formal dining room is perfect for hosting, while the family room beckons warmth and comfort. The well-appointed kitchen is just waiting for the creation of fabulous meals, and a convenient half bath finishes off the main level. Ascend the staircase to the upper level. The primary bedroom, a retreat in itself, boasts an en suite bathroom for moments of relaxation and indulgence. Two additional guest bedrooms and a full bathroom ensure ample accommodation options for family and guests. As daylight graces the interiors, panoramic views of rolling hills and majestic mountains unfold, providing a daily spectacle of nature’s beauty. The oversized backyard, adorned with a covered patio, becomes a canvas for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining, offering a perfect blend of tranquility and open-air living. While this home presents a canvas for your imagination, envisioning the transformation of this property into your dream home is both exciting and promising. Embrace the potential, add your personal touch, and turn 3284 Mira Monte Dr. into a sanctuary that reflects your unique style and vision. Welcome home to the art of living beautifully.
